title: Sarah Palin CBS Interviews with Katie Couric with Transcripts
description:
Fairly complete set of the Katie Couric&#039;s interviews with Sarah Palin (and her chaperone McCain) with transcripts.  For those who can&#039;t make figure out what she was talking about during the debate, a debate flowchart is included.
